1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:00:03,236 --> 00:00:04,236
Father.

3
00:00:04,284 --> 00:00:05,719
Please, fulfill Mother's wish.

4
00:00:06,306 --> 00:00:08,241
Her last wish is to be
buried back in Jiangnan.

5
00:00:08,541 --> 00:00:09,843
You love her so much,

6
00:00:10,510 --> 00:00:11,543
why can't you even grant her

7
00:00:11,544 --> 00:00:13,445
such a small request?

8
00:00:13,446 --> 00:00:14,446
Nonsense!

9
00:00:14,614 --> 00:00:16,148
Concubine Chen was my
beloved concubine in life,

10
00:00:16,149 --> 00:00:18,661
so after death, she shall naturally
be buried in the imperial mausoleum.

11
00:00:18,685 --> 00:00:19,652
Matters of life and death

12
00:00:19,653 --> 00:00:21,653
are not for you to act
willfully and capriciously.

13
00:00:22,288 --> 00:00:24,924
It seems Concubine
Chen has truly spoiled you.

14
00:00:25,225 --> 00:00:27,327
You have disappointed me greatly.

15
00:00:28,661 --> 00:00:29,661
Father.

16
00:00:29,829 --> 00:00:31,531
You have more than one beloved concubine,

17
00:00:32,866 --> 00:00:35,478
and the imperial mausoleum contains
more than just Mother as a concubine.

18
00:00:35,502 --> 00:00:36,502
If that's the case,

19
00:00:36,669 --> 00:00:38,014
what harm would it do to have one less?

20
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:38,872
Stop talking.

21
00:00:38,905 --> 00:00:39,706
You...

22
00:00:39,906 --> 00:00:40,707
Father.

23
00:00:40,708 --> 00:00:41,941
Brother is right.

24
00:00:42,475 --> 00:00:44,878
If you truly have genuine
feelings for Mother,

25
00:00:44,944 --> 00:00:46,945
why would you ignore her last wish?

26
00:00:46,946 --> 00:00:47,946
How dare you!

27
00:00:48,448 --> 00:00:50,416
Are you two siblings trying to rebel?

28
00:00:50,417 --> 00:00:51,985
How dare you defy me like this!

29
00:00:52,919 --> 00:00:53,919
Come!

30
00:00:54,254 --> 00:00:55,965
After Concubine Chen's
funeral rites are over,

31
00:00:55,989 --> 00:00:58,768
the Fifth Prince and Sixth Princess
shall be confined to their quarters.

32
00:00:58,792 --> 00:01:00,192
For being so willful and unruly,

33
00:01:00,193 --> 00:01:01,193
and speaking nonsense,

34
00:01:01,394 --> 00:01:05,031
you shall reflect on your mistakes.

35
00:01:22,248 --> 00:01:24,717
During these days of your confinement,

36
00:01:25,185 --> 00:01:27,387
have you reflected on anything?

37
00:01:30,290 --> 00:01:31,991
As a prince of the Daxing Dynasty,

38
00:01:32,325 --> 00:01:33,493
I disregarded my status

39
00:01:33,927 --> 00:01:36,127
and even wanted to have Mother buried
back in Jiangnan.

40
00:01:38,131 --> 00:01:39,411
Father's reprimand is justified.

41
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:43,536
I was indeed too reckless.

42
00:01:45,405 --> 00:01:46,405
Father.

43
00:01:46,506 --> 00:01:48,626
It seems Fifth Brother has
reflected on his mistakes.

44
00:01:48,908 --> 00:01:49,876
He is still young,

45
00:01:49,877 --> 00:01:52,356
and it's understandable that
he made a mistake out of impulse.

46
00:01:53,313 --> 00:01:54,313
Fifth Brother,

47
00:01:54,347 --> 00:01:56,015
quickly thank Father for his grace

48
00:01:56,216 --> 00:01:57,776
in lifting your confinement.

49
00:02:04,491 --> 00:02:05,491
Father,

50
00:02:05,859 --> 00:02:07,260
As a prince,

51
00:02:07,393 --> 00:02:09,772
I should naturally dedicate myself
to the prosperity of Daxing.

52
00:02:09,796 --> 00:02:10,796
Just now,

53
00:02:11,531 --> 00:02:12,599
Brother's proposal,

54
00:02:12,832 --> 00:02:13,967
I think it's feasible.

55
00:02:15,201 --> 00:02:17,003
I am willing to go to
the border to guard it,

56
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:18,430
thus making amends for my mistakes

57
00:02:19,072 --> 00:02:20,232
and sharing Father's worries.

58
00:02:38,291 --> 00:02:41,052
Why did you decide to go to the border
without discussing it with me?

59
00:02:42,095 --> 00:02:43,997
Yin Zhou clearly wants to drive you away

60
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:45,570
so he can take control of the court.

61
00:02:46,132 --> 00:02:48,001
You must not fall for his scheme!

62
00:02:49,068 --> 00:02:50,702
I guessed it in the imperial study.

63
00:02:50,703 --> 00:02:51,703
Then why...

64
00:02:55,475 --> 00:02:56,809
I've only just realized now

65
00:02:57,644 --> 00:02:58,945
that without power in my hands,

66
00:02:59,646 --> 00:03:01,281
even with the identity of a prince,

67
00:03:01,447 --> 00:03:02,927
I can only be at the mercy of others.

68
00:03:03,683 --> 00:03:05,885
I couldn't even fulfill Mother's last wish.

69
00:03:13,693 --> 00:03:14,813
The border is bitterly cold,

70
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,430
and fraught with danger.

71
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:22,702
Is it worth taking such a risk for power?

72
00:03:24,571 --> 00:03:25,605
Is it really worth it?

73
00:03:28,174 --> 00:03:29,374
Do you have a better proposal?

74
00:03:29,642 --> 00:03:30,043
I...

75
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:31,211
My mind is made up.

76
00:03:32,011 --> 00:03:34,091
No matter what you say,
it won't change my decision.

77
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:05,000
"Journey With You"

78
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,400
(Episode 2)

79
00:05:56,756 --> 00:05:57,756
Who's there?

80
00:06:12,004 --> 00:06:13,004
Wait.

81
00:06:16,175 --> 00:06:18,444
What's the rush, Fifth Brother?

82
00:06:18,945 --> 00:06:21,047
I've come to bid farewell
to Concubine Chen.

83
00:06:25,451 --> 00:06:27,686
Today is the day Mother sets off
for the imperial mausoleum.

84
00:06:27,687 --> 00:06:28,767
We can't afford any delays.

85
00:06:30,189 --> 00:06:31,909
Whatever Brother want to talk to me about,

86
00:06:32,091 --> 00:06:33,393
let's discuss it when I return.

87
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:36,229
You may have fooled Father,
but you can't fool me.

88
00:06:36,996 --> 00:06:38,676
I'm afraid the person lying in this coffin

89
00:06:39,065 --> 00:06:40,666
is not Concubine Chen, is she?

90
00:06:47,573 --> 00:06:48,674
Crown Prince.

91
00:06:48,775 --> 00:06:50,519
The body of Her Majesty Concubine Chen
has already been placed in the coffin.

92
00:06:50,543 --> 00:06:51,543
This is true.

93
00:07:05,992 --> 00:07:06,793
Your Highness,

94
00:07:06,859 --> 00:07:07,939
this move is inappropriate.

95
00:07:12,832 --> 00:07:14,367
With Fifth Brother's skills,

96
00:07:14,934 --> 00:07:16,969
I'm afraid he couldn't even kill a chicken.

97
00:07:19,372 --> 00:07:23,643
His move is nothing
more than a sign of guilt.

98
00:07:34,787 --> 00:07:35,888
Yin Qi, you've gone mad!

99
00:07:36,055 --> 00:07:37,222
How dare you lay a hand on me!

100
00:07:37,223 --> 00:07:38,257
These skills and footwork

101
00:07:38,691 --> 00:07:41,170
can only be found in someone
who has been through countless battles.

102
00:07:41,194 --> 00:07:42,194
How could he...

103
00:07:42,628 --> 00:07:43,628
How dare you!

104
00:07:43,863 --> 00:07:44,863
Yin Qi,

105
00:07:44,931 --> 00:07:46,211
you harbor malicious intentions,

106
00:07:46,933 --> 00:07:49,235
and dare to draw your sword against me!

107
00:07:49,569 --> 00:07:51,037
If you're not guilty, then what is it?

108
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:55,741
You insulted my mother!

109
00:07:56,375 --> 00:07:57,877
So what if I'm reckless?

110
00:07:59,011 --> 00:08:00,179
Crown Prince.

111
00:08:00,413 --> 00:08:02,057
Fifth Prince is deeply concerned
about Concubine Chen.

112
00:08:02,081 --> 00:08:03,481
That's why he acted so impulsively.

113
00:08:03,816 --> 00:08:04,816
Fifth Prince,

114
00:08:04,884 --> 00:08:06,964
we can't delay the time
for Concubine Chen's burial.

115
00:08:07,753 --> 00:08:09,255
We should set off quickly.

116
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:18,998
Today, this coffin...

117
00:08:20,633 --> 00:08:22,435
I will open it!

118
00:08:23,202 --> 00:08:24,202
Yin Qi,

119
00:08:24,637 --> 00:08:27,206
you secretly sent a concubine's
body out of the palace.

120
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:29,775
No matter how much Father favors you,

121
00:08:30,042 --> 00:08:31,042
this time,

122
00:08:31,744 --> 00:08:32,812
he won't spare you!

123
00:08:38,284 --> 00:08:39,284
No!

124
00:08:43,523 --> 00:08:43,823
How...

125
00:08:44,323 --> 00:08:45,323
How could it be?

126
00:08:46,025 --> 00:08:47,493
How could Concubine Chen be here?

127
00:08:47,994 --> 00:08:49,095
I clearly...

128
00:08:54,901 --> 00:08:55,901
Look clearly,

129
00:08:56,702 --> 00:08:58,504
who is lying in this coffin,

130
00:08:58,971 --> 00:09:00,373
whether it's my mother or not.

131
00:09:11,083 --> 00:09:13,319
Today, you dared to draw
your sword against me.

132
00:09:13,953 --> 00:09:14,953
This grudge,

133
00:09:15,521 --> 00:09:17,557
I will repay it!

134
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,630
It seems that.

135
00:10:05,714 --> 00:10:08,584
Fifth Prince had planned to "lure the tiger
away from the mountain" from the start.

136
00:10:08,608 --> 00:10:09,608
He deceived Yin Zhou,

137
00:10:10,142 --> 00:10:11,142
and also

138
00:10:11,377 --> 00:10:12,377
deceived the master.

139
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:14,714
He suspects me.

140
00:10:16,816 --> 00:10:18,936
But he's been taking care
of Concubine Chen recently.

141
00:10:19,285 --> 00:10:20,486
Why would he suspect me?

142
00:10:21,954 --> 00:10:23,389
Even the master doesn't know.

143
00:10:23,789 --> 00:10:25,157
I know even less.

144
00:10:26,492 --> 00:10:27,627
Send out two teams,

145
00:10:27,994 --> 00:10:29,794
one to escort Qi to
the imperial mausoleum,

146
00:10:30,429 --> 00:10:31,429
and the other

147
00:10:31,731 --> 00:10:33,411
to escort Concubine Chen back to Jiangnan.

148
00:10:34,133 --> 00:10:35,133
Master,

149
00:10:35,768 --> 00:10:37,469
Fifth Prince didn't even tell you his plan,

150
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:38,550
yet he used it to test you.

151
00:10:38,804 --> 00:10:39,939
He doesn't trust you.

152
00:10:40,439 --> 00:10:41,741
With such distrust,

153
00:10:41,941 --> 00:10:43,342
why do you still protect him?

154
00:10:48,614 --> 00:10:50,654
There must be a spy from
Yin Zhou's side near Qi.

155
00:10:51,317 --> 00:10:52,317
Perhaps,

156
00:10:52,618 --> 00:10:54,578
they'll prepare to backstab at any moment.

157
00:10:56,722 --> 00:10:58,591
It's better to be well-prepared.

158
00:10:58,891 --> 00:10:59,959
A bunch of useless fools!

159
00:11:18,844 --> 00:11:19,884
Forgive me, Your Highness.

160
00:11:24,417 --> 00:11:27,787
Didn't you say Yin Qi secretly sent
Concubine Chen out of the palace?

161
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,502
Well what happened today?

162
00:11:30,156 --> 00:11:32,491
I did receive information from
Duan Yi and Duan Yong,

163
00:11:33,025 --> 00:11:34,359
and the guards at
Shun'an Gate also reported

164
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:36,138
that Yin Qi left the palace
in the middle of the night.

165
00:11:36,162 --> 00:11:37,429
What happened after that,

166
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:38,631
I really don't know.

167
00:11:38,964 --> 00:11:40,564
It's all my fault for being incompetent.

168
00:11:41,233 --> 00:11:43,202
I trusted you so much,

169
00:11:43,335 --> 00:11:45,055
that I was confident in opening the coffin.

170
00:11:45,571 --> 00:11:47,039
But what was the result?

171
00:11:47,633 --> 00:11:49,334
Now I'm confined to my quarters by Father,

172
00:11:50,142 --> 00:11:54,013
and he's even less likely to trust me now.

173
00:11:54,914 --> 00:11:57,283
This matter is truly strange.

174
00:11:58,150 --> 00:12:00,085
Yin Qi wants to send Concubine
Chen back to Jiangnan.

175
00:12:00,086 --> 00:12:01,287
There's no mistake about it.

176
00:12:01,787 --> 00:12:02,787
Could it be that...

177
00:12:03,589 --> 00:12:04,589
he is...

178
00:12:05,591 --> 00:12:06,791
He wants to use Concubine Chen

179
00:12:07,526 --> 00:12:08,728
to frame Your Highness...?

180
00:12:12,431 --> 00:12:14,066
I didn't realize before

181
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,969
that Yin Qi was so scheming.

182
00:12:18,471 --> 00:12:20,840
How dare he play tricks on me!

183
00:12:21,774 --> 00:12:23,809
I'll make sure he has
no place to be buried!

184
00:12:40,993 --> 00:12:41,794
Your Highness,

185
00:12:41,927 --> 00:12:43,095
it's alright.

186
00:12:43,429 --> 00:12:44,596
Before I go back,

187
00:12:44,597 --> 00:12:46,599
I'll find a way to cover up this red mark.

188
00:12:46,899 --> 00:12:48,501
No one else will notice.

189
00:12:50,936 --> 00:12:52,037
I may seem to be

190
00:12:53,105 --> 00:12:55,641
second only to the emperor,

191
00:12:56,342 --> 00:12:58,544
but the only person I can truly trust

192
00:12:59,145 --> 00:13:00,579
is you.

193
00:13:01,347 --> 00:13:03,883
Don't let me down again.

194
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,320
I,

195
00:13:10,389 --> 00:13:12,670
am willing to share Your
Highness's worries and troubles,

196
00:13:13,192 --> 00:13:14,992
even if it means death
a thousand times over.

197
00:13:25,137 --> 00:13:27,373
Now I've changed what
happened in my past life,

198
00:13:28,507 --> 00:13:30,176
sending you back to Jiangnan.

199
00:13:31,143 --> 00:13:34,512
This shows that I can defy
fate and change destiny.

200
00:13:39,389 --> 00:13:40,615
[Fengsun]

201
00:13:41,554 --> 00:13:42,554
Next,

202
00:13:43,322 --> 00:13:46,525
it's time to investigate Yin
Zhou and Su He's rebellion.

203
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:52,243
[Yin Qi]

204
00:14:27,013 --> 00:14:28,013
Mother,

205
00:14:33,105 --> 00:14:34,373
to be honest,

206
00:14:35,441 --> 00:14:36,742
even though I know

207
00:14:37,343 --> 00:14:39,612
that Yanzhi might be the informant,

208
00:14:41,714 --> 00:14:43,549
I still can't believe it.

209
00:14:48,387 --> 00:14:49,387
Mother,

210
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:52,892
can you tell me

211
00:14:54,193 --> 00:14:55,894
what I should do

212
00:14:56,595 --> 00:14:58,330
to make Yanzhi change his ways?

213
00:15:06,305 --> 00:15:07,305
Does it hurt?

214
00:15:09,708 --> 00:15:10,708
Mother,

215
00:15:11,744 --> 00:15:13,279
you know I've come back from rebirth,

216
00:15:14,313 --> 00:15:15,313
right?

217
00:15:33,165 --> 00:15:35,434
If you want to cry, just cry.

218
00:15:37,369 --> 00:15:40,706
There's no one else in
Yonghe Palace but me now.

219
00:15:48,547 --> 00:15:49,547
Qi,

220
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:52,550
cry,

221
00:15:53,385 --> 00:15:54,720
it'll make you feel better.

222
00:16:14,293 --> 00:16:15,293
Qi,

223
00:16:18,774 --> 00:16:19,770
you mentioned last time

224
00:16:20,546 --> 00:16:22,546
you were secretly sending Concubine
Chen out of the palace.

225
00:16:22,815 --> 00:16:23,815
How come I...

226
00:16:23,916 --> 00:16:24,917
You're right.

227
00:16:25,417 --> 00:16:26,752
That move was too risky.

228
00:16:27,619 --> 00:16:29,922
I shouldn't have risked
Mother's body like that.

229
00:16:30,923 --> 00:16:32,624
Now Mother is in the imperial mausoleum,

230
00:16:34,126 --> 00:16:35,794
at least she can rest in peace.

231
00:16:55,547 --> 00:16:58,317
During the three years I was
away from the capital in my past life,

232
00:16:58,684 --> 00:17:00,185
what exactly happened?

233
00:17:00,986 --> 00:17:04,223
When did he start colluding with Yin Zhou?

234
00:17:05,224 --> 00:17:05,991
Qi,

235
00:17:05,992 --> 00:17:07,469
the ice chest and agarwood you wanted,

236
00:17:07,493 --> 00:17:08,794
I've sent someone to buy them.

237
00:17:20,539 --> 00:17:22,219
In my past life, when I was at the border,

238
00:17:22,374 --> 00:17:24,109
we faced a shortage of food and supplies.

239
00:17:24,243 --> 00:17:25,443
The Central Plains merchant caravan

240
00:17:25,444 --> 00:17:27,046
that helped us relieve our urgent needs

241
00:17:27,379 --> 00:17:29,114
also used this sign as their emblem.

242
00:17:30,282 --> 00:17:30,716
At that time,

243
00:17:31,283 --> 00:17:33,152
Yanzhi must have secretly helped me.

244
00:17:33,752 --> 00:17:34,353
But how...

245
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,560
did he come to know
the people in the caravan?

246
00:17:44,730 --> 00:17:45,164
Your Highness,

247
00:17:45,731 --> 00:17:47,266
My brother and I have discovered that.

248
00:17:47,633 --> 00:17:50,335
Su He's confidants have been in
contact with the capital all along,

249
00:17:50,569 --> 00:17:52,049
and there have been illegal dealings.

250
00:17:52,204 --> 00:17:54,706
But we still need to investigate
the specific addresses.

251
00:17:56,989 --> 00:18:00,593
Yanzhi's uncle is also a formidable figure.

252
00:18:10,322 --> 00:18:11,322
This mark

253
00:18:11,857 --> 00:18:14,017
should be the emblem of a
certain chamber of commerce.

254
00:18:14,193 --> 00:18:16,728
Find any relevant information or clues

255
00:18:17,563 --> 00:18:18,797
and report back immediately.

256
00:18:19,031 --> 00:18:20,031
Yes.

257
00:18:24,603 --> 00:18:25,771
Don't alert the enemy.

258
00:18:26,338 --> 00:18:28,207
My brother and I know what to do.

259
00:18:32,845 --> 00:18:33,845
Your Highness!

260
00:18:33,979 --> 00:18:34,979
Your Highness!

261
00:18:35,414 --> 00:18:35,814
Your Highness!

262
00:18:35,814 --> 00:18:36,315
Qi!

263
00:18:36,515 --> 00:18:37,515
Qi!

264
00:18:37,950 --> 00:18:38,750
Duan Yi, Duan Yong!

265
00:18:38,784 --> 00:18:40,085
Quickly, call Doctor Bai!

266
00:18:40,552 --> 00:18:41,019
Go!

267
00:18:41,019 --> 00:18:41,320
Okay.

268
00:18:41,386 --> 00:18:42,386
Okay.

269
00:18:43,522 --> 00:18:44,522
Qi...

270
00:18:51,797 --> 00:18:53,141
His Highness has been overworked,

271
00:18:53,165 --> 00:18:54,165
running back and forth,

272
00:18:54,399 --> 00:18:55,879
which is why the fever won't subside.

273
00:18:59,738 --> 00:19:01,607
The clothes are soaked with sweat.

274
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:04,109
We need to change into
clean clothes immediately.

275
00:19:05,144 --> 00:19:06,210
Your Highness, lie still.

276
00:19:06,211 --> 00:19:07,546
Let me do it.

277
00:19:13,318 --> 00:19:14,686
Yanzhi!

278
00:19:18,423 --> 00:19:19,423
Yanzhi!

279
00:19:23,162 --> 00:19:24,396
Let me do it.

280
00:19:54,159 --> 00:19:55,159
Water.

281
00:19:56,428 --> 00:19:57,428
Water.

282
00:19:59,898 --> 00:20:00,898
Here.

283
00:20:02,434 --> 00:20:03,434
Drink slowly.

284
00:20:03,535 --> 00:20:04,535
Don't choke.

285
00:20:17,416 --> 00:20:19,151
You've been here with me the whole time.

286
00:20:20,719 --> 00:20:21,719
Yes.

287
00:20:22,955 --> 00:20:24,323
It's good that you're awake.

288
00:20:24,923 --> 00:20:27,024
Doctor Bai prescribed some medicine.

289
00:20:27,025 --> 00:20:28,326
I've sent someone to prepare it.

290
00:20:28,327 --> 00:20:29,728
I'll go check if it's ready.

291
00:20:30,596 --> 00:20:31,596
No.

292
00:20:33,532 --> 00:20:34,600
Don't go.

293
00:20:35,434 --> 00:20:37,336
I want you to stay with me.

294
00:20:40,903 --> 00:20:43,008
I'm just going to check
if the medicine is ready.

295
00:20:43,342 --> 00:20:45,811
Why do you say it as if I
won't come back?

296
00:20:47,946 --> 00:20:49,414
I'm just afraid...

297
00:20:50,816 --> 00:20:52,951
afraid that you've changed from before,

298
00:20:53,819 --> 00:20:55,420
and I know nothing about it.

299
00:21:00,425 --> 00:21:01,936
You've clearly recovered from the fever,

300
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,328
yet you're still talking nonsense.

301
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,030
A few days ago,

302
00:21:06,932 --> 00:21:08,634
I saw you go to Mingde Palace.

303
00:21:10,002 --> 00:21:12,204
Don't you hate the Crown Prince the most?

304
00:21:13,905 --> 00:21:15,385
The way the Crown Prince looks at you

305
00:21:16,675 --> 00:21:18,343
must mean he has ulterior motives.

306
00:21:19,011 --> 00:21:20,291
What's going on between you two?

307
00:21:20,946 --> 00:21:22,247
What secrets are you hiding?

308
00:21:22,881 --> 00:21:23,881
I just...

309
00:21:24,416 --> 00:21:26,456
saw Yin Zhou being
disrespectful to Concubine Chen,

310
00:21:26,918 --> 00:21:28,720
and wanted to avenge you.

311
00:21:33,592 --> 00:21:35,093
Now that I'm awake,

312
00:21:35,994 --> 00:21:37,629
you don't have to stay here anymore.

313
00:21:42,034 --> 00:21:43,034
Brother Yanzhi,

314
00:21:44,223 --> 00:21:45,157
rest assured,

315
00:21:45,203 --> 00:21:47,973
I'll make sure the Crown
Prince takes the medicine.

316
00:21:50,542 --> 00:21:51,542
Very well.

317
00:21:52,144 --> 00:21:53,578
Then I'll take my leave.

318
00:22:07,492 --> 00:22:08,972
What's wrong with you, Crown Brother?

319
00:22:09,161 --> 00:22:10,828
When you were on the verge of death,

320
00:22:10,829 --> 00:22:12,798
you wouldn't let go of
Brother Yanzhi's hand.

321
00:22:13,098 --> 00:22:14,232
Now that you're better,

322
00:22:14,833 --> 00:22:16,335
you want to send him away.

323
00:22:17,169 --> 00:22:19,236
Fortunately, Brother
Yanzhi has a good temper,

324
00:22:19,237 --> 00:22:20,439
or he wouldn't have let it go.

325
00:22:22,774 --> 00:22:24,209
The more you rely on someone,

326
00:22:24,643 --> 00:22:27,012
the deeper you'll be hurt in the end.

327
00:22:30,816 --> 00:22:33,118
The current Khan of the Talhan, Tiele Suhe,

328
00:22:33,418 --> 00:22:35,020
is Yanzhi's elder brother.

329
00:22:35,754 --> 00:22:37,322
The reason he became the Khan

330
00:22:37,799 --> 00:22:40,792
is entirely due to his father's,
Harichagai's, past prestige.

331
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,288
Su He considers himself highly capable,

332
00:22:43,762 --> 00:22:44,762
so naturally,

333
00:22:44,796 --> 00:22:46,732
he's unwilling to be
inferior to his nephew.

334
00:22:49,401 --> 00:22:50,401
No wonder...

335
00:22:51,002 --> 00:22:53,705
Yanzhi went to seek refuge with his uncle.

336
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:57,180
Yanzhi has been in the capital for years,

337
00:22:57,409 --> 00:22:59,544
and is no longer the prince of the Talhan.

338
00:22:59,945 --> 00:23:02,314
It's only natural for him
to seek refuge with Su He.

339
00:23:02,881 --> 00:23:04,483
I heard today that.

340
00:23:04,983 --> 00:23:07,018
Su He led his troops to
attack the Jurchen tribe,

341
00:23:07,819 --> 00:23:10,589
and a large number of refugees
are flooding towards our border.

342
00:23:14,826 --> 00:23:15,826
Your Highness,

343
00:23:15,894 --> 00:23:16,862
this is a great opportunity

344
00:23:16,863 --> 00:23:18,530
to send Yin Qi to the border!

345
00:23:26,505 --> 00:23:29,508
You truly deserve the
training I've given you.

346
00:23:40,886 --> 00:23:41,520
Your Highness,

347
00:23:41,521 --> 00:23:43,021
This bird is really interesting.

348
00:23:43,989 --> 00:23:45,557
The interesting part is yet to come.

349
00:23:47,092 --> 00:23:47,592
Your Highness,

350
00:23:47,593 --> 00:23:49,294
let's continue over there.

351
00:24:00,505 --> 00:24:01,940
Crown Prince,

352
00:24:09,114 --> 00:24:11,383
This cloak is quite unique.

353
00:24:13,118 --> 00:24:14,786
Your Highness may have forgotten recently

354
00:24:15,153 --> 00:24:17,088
that you and I are allies,

355
00:24:17,389 --> 00:24:19,791
I'm not a servant who follow your orders.

356
00:24:20,559 --> 00:24:24,696
A hostage dares to stand
on equal footing with me?

357
00:24:44,549 --> 00:24:45,984
The things of the Talhan

358
00:24:46,585 --> 00:24:48,520
naturally belong to our Daxing.

359
00:24:50,722 --> 00:24:52,123
The people of the Talhan

360
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:55,360
are ultimately servants of our Daxing.

361
00:24:57,762 --> 00:25:01,166
You and Yin Qi caused me
to be confined for half a month.

362
00:25:01,633 --> 00:25:02,634
I haven't

363
00:25:03,001 --> 00:25:05,637
settled this score with you yet.

364
00:25:10,542 --> 00:25:11,542
Let go of Yanzhi!

365
00:25:17,415 --> 00:25:19,584
Fifth Brother has recovered quickly.

366
00:25:20,285 --> 00:25:21,285
It seems

367
00:25:22,687 --> 00:25:25,156
he was well taken care of.

368
00:25:30,528 --> 00:25:31,528
Let's go.

369
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:33,231
I'm disciplining a hostage.

370
00:25:33,732 --> 00:25:36,034
When did it become your place to interfere?

371
00:25:40,005 --> 00:25:42,245
Crown Brother, you may
discipline your own palace staff,

372
00:25:42,507 --> 00:25:44,142
and I have nothing to say about that.

373
00:25:44,309 --> 00:25:45,911
But Yanzhi is mine.

374
00:25:46,344 --> 00:25:48,013
Even if he has angered the Crown Prince,

375
00:25:48,547 --> 00:25:50,014
it should be me who deals with him.

376
00:25:50,015 --> 00:25:50,348
You...

377
00:25:50,348 --> 00:25:51,348
What about me?

378
00:25:55,086 --> 00:25:56,488
Crown Prince.

379
00:25:56,721 --> 00:25:57,721
Fifth Prince.

380
00:25:58,323 --> 00:26:00,883
The Emperor wants you both to
come to discuss political affairs.

381
00:26:00,992 --> 00:26:02,993
He is waiting in the imperial study now.

382
00:26:02,994 --> 00:26:05,530
Come with me to see him at once.

383
00:26:13,939 --> 00:26:15,239
Today is the day that, in my past life,

384
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:16,774
separated Yanzhi and me for three years

385
00:26:16,775 --> 00:26:18,295
and led us into a desperate situation.

386
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:20,445
This day has come again in the end.

387
00:26:20,845 --> 00:26:21,845
Qi,

388
00:26:22,047 --> 00:26:23,047
promise me

389
00:26:23,615 --> 00:26:24,883
no matter what happens,

390
00:26:25,383 --> 00:26:26,484
you must stay calm.

391
00:26:29,788 --> 00:26:30,788
Don't worry.

392
00:26:41,566 --> 00:26:42,566
A hostage

393
00:26:43,234 --> 00:26:45,034
in exchange for ten
years of border stability

394
00:26:45,236 --> 00:26:46,876
is already a great favor from our Daxing.

395
00:26:47,945 --> 00:26:50,951
I didn't expect that Su He would
bide his time and build up his strength

396
00:26:50,976 --> 00:26:53,678
over these years and
continuously expand his influence.

397
00:26:54,946 --> 00:26:56,314
Because of his ambition,

398
00:26:56,715 --> 00:26:59,517
our Daxing's border has
been plunged into misery.

399
00:27:02,087 --> 00:27:03,288
Your son believes that

400
00:27:03,488 --> 00:27:04,488
we should

401
00:27:04,689 --> 00:27:07,692
offer some assistance to Su He
in conquering the Jurchen tribe.

402
00:27:07,826 --> 00:27:09,761
Once Su He unifies the grassland tribes,

403
00:27:10,161 --> 00:27:12,998
the Talhan will ultimately be
a vassal state of our Daxing.

404
00:27:13,164 --> 00:27:16,301
Su He will surely remember the
kindness of Father Emperor's support

405
00:27:16,368 --> 00:27:19,504
and will surely submit to our Daxing.

406
00:27:21,439 --> 00:27:22,439
Your son's idea

407
00:27:22,641 --> 00:27:24,843
is exactly the opposite
of the Crown Prince's.

408
00:27:27,946 --> 00:27:28,946
Get out!

409
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:30,191
All of you, get out of here!

410
00:27:30,215 --> 00:27:31,716
A bunch of useless fools!

411
00:27:51,436 --> 00:27:52,570
I have warned you that

412
00:27:53,271 --> 00:27:54,472
only the incompetent

413
00:27:54,806 --> 00:27:56,107
would lose their temper.

414
00:27:56,775 --> 00:27:57,509
Mother Queen,

415
00:27:57,709 --> 00:27:58,709
you said that.

416
00:27:59,177 --> 00:28:01,713
Father Emperor only dotes
on Yin Qi because of Concubine Chen.

417
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:03,180
But today, it seems that.

418
00:28:03,515 --> 00:28:05,250
Father Emperor trusts Yin Qi quite a bit.

419
00:28:06,251 --> 00:28:08,086
The words Yin Qi spoke
in the imperial study.

420
00:28:08,286 --> 00:28:09,926
Father Emperor actually listened to them.

421
00:28:12,323 --> 00:28:13,323
Your father

422
00:28:13,591 --> 00:28:16,361
is merely using Yin Qi to suppress you.

423
00:28:16,528 --> 00:28:17,528
Even so,

424
00:28:18,063 --> 00:28:19,664
Father Emperor is too biased.

425
00:28:21,266 --> 00:28:22,943
Father Emperor made me confined to
my quarters for half a month

426
00:28:22,967 --> 00:28:24,602
because of Concubine Chen.

427
00:28:25,003 --> 00:28:26,003
Yin Qi...

428
00:28:26,104 --> 00:28:27,982
Yin Qi even drew his sword
against me in the palace,

429
00:28:28,006 --> 00:28:29,486
yet Father Emperor didn't punish him.

430
00:28:33,278 --> 00:28:35,480
Yin Qi has framed me several times

431
00:28:35,914 --> 00:28:37,314
and always shows off his sharpness.

432
00:28:37,849 --> 00:28:38,849
He actually

433
00:28:39,517 --> 00:28:40,952
has been pretending for so long.

434
00:28:44,189 --> 00:28:45,190
I have forgotten that

435
00:28:46,357 --> 00:28:47,592
in the past, Concubine Chen

436
00:28:47,959 --> 00:28:50,199
was the best at hiding her
sharpness and staying humble.

437
00:28:51,696 --> 00:28:53,731
Yin Qi was raised by his mother concubine.

438
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:57,001
Since Yin Qi

439
00:28:57,535 --> 00:28:59,571
is unwilling to leave
the capital voluntarily,

440
00:29:00,939 --> 00:29:02,974
can't you use some means

441
00:29:03,775 --> 00:29:04,876
to force him to leave?

442
00:29:21,226 --> 00:29:22,226
Qi,

443
00:29:22,627 --> 00:29:24,495
What did the Emperor
summon you and Yin Zhou for?

444
00:29:24,496 --> 00:29:25,497
Why did it take so long?

445
00:29:30,535 --> 00:29:32,570
Your uncle insists on
attacking the Jurchen tribe,

446
00:29:32,971 --> 00:29:35,206
so our Daxing's border is
naturally suffering as well.

447
00:29:36,508 --> 00:29:37,709
Father Emperor was furious

448
00:29:38,109 --> 00:29:40,411
and asked me and Yin Zhou
what countermeasures we had.

449
00:29:45,817 --> 00:29:46,817
Yin Zhou suggested

450
00:29:47,352 --> 00:29:48,352
that I lead the troops

451
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:50,020
to garrison the border.

452
00:29:50,021 --> 00:29:51,021
What?

453
00:29:53,625 --> 00:29:54,025
Qi,

454
00:29:54,025 --> 00:29:54,793
Be gentle.

455
00:29:54,794 --> 00:29:56,474
Are you applying medicine or poisoning me?

456
00:29:56,561 --> 00:29:58,029
This minor injury has become worse

457
00:29:58,296 --> 00:29:59,497
after your treatment.

458
00:30:00,498 --> 00:30:01,498
Your hand,

459
00:30:01,533 --> 00:30:02,533
is having a tough year.

460
00:30:03,334 --> 00:30:04,334
It was almost healed,

461
00:30:04,702 --> 00:30:05,902
but now it's split open again.

462
00:30:06,805 --> 00:30:07,805
If your hand is injured,

463
00:30:08,740 --> 00:30:09,740
I'll support you.

464
00:30:12,377 --> 00:30:13,377
Anyway,

465
00:30:13,812 --> 00:30:14,972
the border is very dangerous.

466
00:30:15,013 --> 00:30:16,247
You must not go.

467
00:30:18,316 --> 00:30:20,083
My Crown Brother is trying every means

468
00:30:20,084 --> 00:30:21,719
to drive me out of the capital.

469
00:30:22,687 --> 00:30:24,422
I naturally won't do as he wishes.

470
00:30:28,639 --> 00:30:29,974
Of course I can't go.

471
00:30:30,528 --> 00:30:32,596
Otherwise, how can I know
what happened between you

472
00:30:32,597 --> 00:30:34,432
in these three years?

473
00:30:47,745 --> 00:30:49,280
I have long predicted that

474
00:30:49,547 --> 00:30:50,824
you would come to see me tonight.

475
00:30:50,848 --> 00:30:52,917
Just as I expected.

476
00:30:53,518 --> 00:30:54,518
Coincidentally,

477
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:57,121
I also have something to ask you.

478
00:30:58,089 --> 00:30:59,649
Your Highness should be very clear that

479
00:30:59,951 --> 00:31:00,951
between us

480
00:31:01,352 --> 00:31:02,352
is mutual benefaction.

481
00:31:03,005 --> 00:31:04,827
After the matter is
accomplished, what I seek

482
00:31:05,296 --> 00:31:06,564
is to save Qi's life.

483
00:31:07,932 --> 00:31:08,932
Given that,

484
00:31:09,734 --> 00:31:12,203
why does Your Highness
force him to go to the border?

485
00:31:14,105 --> 00:31:15,707
Don't you notice that.

486
00:31:16,140 --> 00:31:18,409
Yin Qi recently

487
00:31:18,716 --> 00:31:20,516
is a completely different
person from before?

488
00:31:23,781 --> 00:31:26,684
You are planning wholeheartedly
for your Fifth Prince,

489
00:31:27,318 --> 00:31:29,554
but Yin Qi doesn't appreciate it at all.

490
00:31:30,521 --> 00:31:32,089
On the day Concubine Chen
was interred in the imperial mausoleum,

491
00:31:32,090 --> 00:31:33,758
even you were deceived.

492
00:31:40,298 --> 00:31:41,298
How about...

493
00:31:44,736 --> 00:31:47,138
I give you a better choice:

494
00:31:47,639 --> 00:31:48,940
abandon Yin Qi

495
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:51,409
and completely join my camp.

496
00:31:52,176 --> 00:31:53,544
You should understand that

497
00:31:54,445 --> 00:31:55,847
such a choice

498
00:31:56,881 --> 00:31:59,083
is the right one for you.

499
00:32:01,425 --> 00:32:02,985
My original intention has never changed

500
00:32:04,022 --> 00:32:05,223
and it will never change.

501
00:32:07,025 --> 00:32:08,493
As for whether my choice is correct,

502
00:32:10,328 --> 00:32:11,930
only I can decide.

503
00:32:45,530 --> 00:32:46,530
Your Highness,

504
00:32:46,965 --> 00:32:48,800
I have followed your orders

505
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:50,667
and spread the news

506
00:32:50,668 --> 00:32:52,437
that Yin Qi is going
to garrison the border.

507
00:32:53,604 --> 00:32:54,972
Soon,

508
00:32:56,541 --> 00:32:58,776
everyone in the imperial city will know.

509
00:33:00,912 --> 00:33:04,015
Since they won't listen to my wishes,

510
00:33:04,148 --> 00:33:09,554
I'll let Yin Qi experience
what it's like to go to the border.

511
00:33:49,594 --> 00:33:50,495
Right now,

512
00:33:50,496 --> 00:33:51,561
I have neither real power

513
00:33:51,562 --> 00:33:52,563
nor military forces.

514
00:33:52,964 --> 00:33:55,245
The only thing I can hold
onto is Father Emperor's trust.

515
00:33:55,533 --> 00:33:56,933
I must strike while the iron is hot

516
00:33:57,168 --> 00:33:59,408
and make Father Emperor
believe that what I say is true.

517
00:33:59,504 --> 00:34:01,839
Only then can I have a chance
to compete with Yin Zhou.

518
00:34:08,446 --> 00:34:09,446
Qi,

519
00:34:09,847 --> 00:34:11,215
Didn't you refuse the Emperor?

520
00:34:11,749 --> 00:34:13,427
Why is it being spread all over the palace

521
00:34:13,451 --> 00:34:14,819
that you are going to the border?

522
00:34:16,421 --> 00:34:17,581
It's being spread everywhere.

523
00:34:18,222 --> 00:34:19,222
That's interesting.

524
00:34:21,526 --> 00:34:23,046
It seems that Yin Zhou is behind this.

525
00:34:24,362 --> 00:34:25,722
On that day in the imperial study,

526
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:27,331
how did you refuse the Emperor?

527
00:34:28,833 --> 00:34:29,901
Your son believes that

528
00:34:30,301 --> 00:34:31,936
we must divide his forces

529
00:34:32,737 --> 00:34:34,605
and maintain a balance among the tribes.

530
00:34:35,006 --> 00:34:36,941
If he really conquers the Jurchen tribe,

531
00:34:37,041 --> 00:34:38,509
his morale will surely soar

532
00:34:38,709 --> 00:34:40,549
and he will raise troops
to invade our Daxing.

533
00:34:40,984 --> 00:34:42,252
A mere Khan!

534
00:34:42,847 --> 00:34:43,980
Even if you give him ten times the courage,

535
00:34:43,981 --> 00:34:45,917
he wouldn't dare to do
anything to our Daxing.

536
00:34:46,284 --> 00:34:47,752
The Crown Brother is wrong.

537
00:34:48,753 --> 00:34:49,753
Every move of the Talhan

538
00:34:50,588 --> 00:34:51,588
will affect our Daxing

539
00:34:51,589 --> 00:34:53,149
and the interests of the border people.

540
00:34:54,292 --> 00:34:56,170
Father Emperor has always loved
his people like his own children.

541
00:34:56,194 --> 00:34:57,895
As Father Emperor's subjects,

542
00:34:58,096 --> 00:34:59,376
we should be like Father Emperor

543
00:34:59,564 --> 00:35:01,004
and consider the people's interests.

544
00:35:03,234 --> 00:35:04,368
My son Qi has

545
00:35:04,735 --> 00:35:06,170
made a lot of progress recently.

546
00:35:07,638 --> 00:35:08,840
I am very pleased.

547
00:35:10,708 --> 00:35:11,709
To be honest,

548
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:13,110
your son has been busy

549
00:35:13,511 --> 00:35:15,556
with Mother Concubine's
funeral in the past few days

550
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:18,100
and hasn't been able to
come to pay respects to Father Emperor.

551
00:35:19,383 --> 00:35:20,383
Today,

552
00:35:20,585 --> 00:35:21,853
your son has a game of Go

553
00:35:22,053 --> 00:35:23,554
of which he would ask
Father Emperor for advice on.

554
00:35:26,157 --> 00:35:27,358
If that's the case,

555
00:35:28,119 --> 00:35:29,119
Son Zhou,

556
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,461
you may withdraw first.

557
00:35:33,898 --> 00:35:34,898
Yes.

558
00:35:39,637 --> 00:35:40,637
I have heard that

559
00:35:41,339 --> 00:35:42,339
a few days ago,

560
00:35:42,473 --> 00:35:44,754
when you were sending Mother
Concubine out of the palace,

561
00:35:44,976 --> 00:35:46,911
before you even reached the Sheng'an Gate,

562
00:35:47,445 --> 00:35:49,013
Zhou stopped you.

563
00:35:53,929 --> 00:35:55,319
Those guards at the gate

564
00:35:55,786 --> 00:35:58,155
are very loyal to Zhou.

565
00:35:58,756 --> 00:36:01,292
They even report the whereabouts
of the princes one by one.

566
00:36:13,938 --> 00:36:14,939
Playing small tricks,

567
00:36:15,339 --> 00:36:16,459
but guarding the great path.

568
00:36:16,807 --> 00:36:20,011
Your vision should be
beyond this chessboard.

569
00:36:20,545 --> 00:36:23,114
Do you understand what my meaning is?

570
00:36:26,184 --> 00:36:27,885
Your son heeds Father Emperor's teachings.

571
00:36:30,988 --> 00:36:31,988
You also agree

572
00:36:32,056 --> 00:36:33,336
with me dealing with your uncle.

573
00:36:33,858 --> 00:36:35,593
Aren't you worried about your people?

574
00:36:38,195 --> 00:36:40,097
From the standpoint of our Daxing,

575
00:36:40,565 --> 00:36:41,966
this is the best choice.

576
00:36:42,967 --> 00:36:43,967
Moreover,

577
00:36:44,502 --> 00:36:45,703
if Su He becomes too powerful,

578
00:36:46,737 --> 00:36:47,872
it may not be a good thing

579
00:36:48,105 --> 00:36:49,206
for my people either.

580
00:36:51,242 --> 00:36:51,676
Actually,

581
00:36:52,243 --> 00:36:53,377
I have a follow-up plan.

582
00:36:54,579 --> 00:36:55,579
Tell me about it.

583
00:36:57,014 --> 00:36:58,225
The border between the
Talhan and our Daxing

584
00:36:58,249 --> 00:36:59,217
is plagued by rampant smuggling

585
00:36:59,218 --> 00:37:00,498
that has been difficult to stop.

586
00:37:00,718 --> 00:37:02,253
I want to take this opportunity

587
00:37:02,787 --> 00:37:03,867
to reorganize the Silk Road

588
00:37:04,288 --> 00:37:06,524
and firmly control the border trade.

589
00:37:08,526 --> 00:37:10,246
It seems that our Qi has really grown up.

590
00:37:11,462 --> 00:37:12,462
Waging war

591
00:37:12,496 --> 00:37:13,898
requires provisions and money.

592
00:37:14,465 --> 00:37:15,533
Su He lacks money

593
00:37:15,866 --> 00:37:17,578
and will find it difficult
to cause trouble again.

594
00:37:17,602 --> 00:37:19,169
If we can really reorganize
the border trade ports

595
00:37:19,170 --> 00:37:20,170
and reduce smuggling,

596
00:37:20,271 --> 00:37:22,707
it will be a good thing for
the border people as well.

597
00:37:31,616 --> 00:37:33,217
Qi and that hostage

598
00:37:33,484 --> 00:37:35,052
really said that?

599
00:37:35,586 --> 00:37:37,688
I heard it clearly.

600
00:37:39,457 --> 00:37:40,992
If Qi does this,

601
00:37:41,092 --> 00:37:43,594
it can dampen Zhou's arrogance.

602
00:37:43,861 --> 00:37:44,862
That hostage

603
00:37:45,162 --> 00:37:47,498
is indeed a person who knows the times.

604
00:37:48,065 --> 00:37:50,501
It's all thanks to the
Emperor's good upbringing.

605
00:37:53,604 --> 00:37:54,739
You should know by now.

606
00:37:55,239 --> 00:37:56,239
I also want to be the one

607
00:37:56,540 --> 00:37:58,009
holding the reigns.

608
00:38:01,012 --> 00:38:02,012
Qi,

609
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:04,582
you never cared about court affairs before,

610
00:38:05,383 --> 00:38:06,684
and had no interest in power.

611
00:38:08,252 --> 00:38:09,492
Is it because of Concubine Chen

612
00:38:12,289 --> 00:38:13,624
or something else

613
00:38:15,026 --> 00:38:16,746
that has made you so different from before?

614
00:38:23,934 --> 00:38:25,670
Even if I've changed from before,

615
00:38:26,804 --> 00:38:27,804
can you

616
00:38:28,806 --> 00:38:30,441
treat the current me with sincerity?

617
00:38:39,984 --> 00:38:40,984
Brother,

618
00:38:41,385 --> 00:38:41,852
Brother!

619
00:38:41,852 --> 00:38:42,852
Are you really going to...

620
00:38:49,093 --> 00:38:50,093
the border?

621
00:38:57,134 --> 00:38:58,494
Why are you dressed as a boy again

622
00:38:58,903 --> 00:38:59,903
and making such a fuss?

623
00:39:00,604 --> 00:39:02,124
You don't look like a princess at all.

624
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:04,340
Brother,

625
00:39:04,875 --> 00:39:06,142
just take me out to play!

626
00:39:06,143 --> 00:39:08,078
I heard the Zhouqiao Night
Market is opening today,

627
00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:09,146
it must be so much fun!

628
00:39:15,405 --> 00:39:17,687
The Empress scolded me again today.

629
00:39:17,688 --> 00:39:18,888
If I can't get out of the palace again,

630
00:39:18,889 --> 00:39:20,691
I'll suffocate to death in this palace!

631
00:39:21,525 --> 00:39:23,294
Don't talk nonsense about dying.

632
00:39:25,996 --> 00:39:27,431
Qi has been weak lately,

633
00:39:27,698 --> 00:39:28,698
he can't go out.

634
00:39:29,467 --> 00:39:30,787
Since Heshu wants to go so badly,

635
00:39:31,035 --> 00:39:32,035
I'll go with you then.

636
00:39:32,603 --> 00:39:33,170
Good.

637
00:39:33,337 --> 00:39:34,205
As long as I can get out of the palace,

638
00:39:34,206 --> 00:39:35,606
it doesn't matter who goes with me.

639
00:39:44,081 --> 00:39:45,081
Your Highness,

640
00:39:45,649 --> 00:39:47,417
Ziming has found out about
Su He's smuggling caravan,

641
00:39:47,418 --> 00:39:49,098
and the place where
they trade in the capital.

642
00:39:49,387 --> 00:39:50,627
It's at the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

643
00:39:51,088 --> 00:39:51,689
Additionally,

644
00:39:51,690 --> 00:39:53,356
the owner of the Piaoxiang Pavilion,

645
00:39:53,357 --> 00:39:55,168
looks like a merchant
from the Central Plains,

646
00:39:55,192 --> 00:39:57,394
but in fact, he was once a
subordinate of Harichagai.

647
00:39:59,263 --> 00:40:00,264
The Piaoxiang Pavilion

648
00:40:00,965 --> 00:40:03,033
is the tavern where Yanzhi often goes.

649
00:40:04,535 --> 00:40:05,535
Harichagai,

650
00:40:05,669 --> 00:40:06,669
Yanzhi's father.

651
00:40:07,938 --> 00:40:09,418
The mark I asked you to investigate,

652
00:40:09,473 --> 00:40:10,873
is it also related to this caravan?

653
00:40:11,475 --> 00:40:13,355
Your subordinate was
just about to report this.

654
00:40:13,944 --> 00:40:14,845
That emblem

655
00:40:14,846 --> 00:40:17,248
is the symbol of Su He's smuggling caravan.

656
00:40:18,182 --> 00:40:18,749
Furthermore,

657
00:40:19,176 --> 00:40:21,712
their caravan has always kept a low profile,

658
00:40:22,052 --> 00:40:23,492
never making friends with merchants.

659
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:28,001
We'll continue to investigate
the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

660
00:40:28,025 --> 00:40:29,427
Don't miss any information.

661
00:40:30,227 --> 00:40:30,995
Your Highness, rest assured.

662
00:40:30,996 --> 00:40:34,098
Ziming has already sent people to observe
around the Piaoxiang Pavilion at all times.

663
00:40:34,099 --> 00:40:35,331
If there's any situation,

664
00:40:35,332 --> 00:40:37,092
they'll report to Your
Highness immediately.

665
00:40:40,838 --> 00:40:41,906
Moreover,

666
00:40:42,306 --> 00:40:43,741
Su He's dominance

667
00:40:44,475 --> 00:40:46,811
may not be a good thing for our people.

668
00:40:48,245 --> 00:40:50,915
In his past life, Yanzhi
worked for Su He and Yin Zhou,

669
00:40:51,215 --> 00:40:52,650
betraying his father and Daxing.

670
00:40:53,217 --> 00:40:55,286
But in the end, he was
killed by his own people.

671
00:40:56,153 --> 00:40:56,854
Could it be that.

672
00:40:57,021 --> 00:40:58,889
Su He has been
blackmailing Yanzhi all along,

673
00:40:59,223 --> 00:41:01,258
so Yanzhi agrees with my idea

674
00:41:01,598 --> 00:41:02,733
to restrain Su He?

675
00:41:12,203 --> 00:41:12,636
Young Master Pei,

676
00:41:12,870 --> 00:41:13,947
it's been a long time since you last came.

677
00:41:13,971 --> 00:41:14,672
Why do you have time to come today?

678
00:41:14,672 --> 00:41:15,072
Waiter!

679
00:41:15,372 --> 00:41:16,806
Bring me the best wine and

680
00:41:16,807 --> 00:41:18,609
the best dishes in your place!

681
00:41:22,847 --> 00:41:23,614
Coming right up, sir!

682
00:41:23,614 --> 00:41:23,814
Come in,

683
00:41:24,014 --> 00:41:25,014
please.

684
00:41:31,021 --> 00:41:32,021
Try this.

685
00:41:32,189 --> 00:41:33,224
It's all delicious.

686
00:41:33,591 --> 00:41:34,591
Brother Yanzhi,

687
00:41:34,825 --> 00:41:37,345
have you noticed that
Brother has been acting strangely lately?

688
00:41:37,561 --> 00:41:39,028
You're with him every day,

689
00:41:39,029 --> 00:41:39,930
haven't you noticed

690
00:41:39,931 --> 00:41:41,565
anything special about him?

691
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:44,068
Even you can see it.

692
00:41:45,302 --> 00:41:46,402
If it were before,

693
00:41:46,403 --> 00:41:47,971
Brother would definitely beg Father

694
00:41:47,972 --> 00:41:49,673
to bury Mother back in Jiangnan.

695
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:52,276
But now he's holding back,

696
00:41:52,676 --> 00:41:54,178
as if he's a different person.

697
00:41:55,212 --> 00:41:57,181
"Even if I've changed from before,

698
00:41:57,915 --> 00:41:58,915
can you

699
00:41:59,623 --> 00:42:01,592
treat the current me with sincerity?"

700
00:42:08,292 --> 00:42:09,412
What are you thinking about?

701
00:42:12,296 --> 00:42:13,296
Nothing.

702
00:42:18,469 --> 00:42:19,803
Don't worry, Brother Yanzhi.

703
00:42:20,371 --> 00:42:22,206
The fact that you like my brother,

704
00:42:24,675 --> 00:42:25,675
even though I know it,

705
00:42:25,876 --> 00:42:27,778
I'll keep it a secret for you.

706
00:42:31,015 --> 00:42:32,015
Sixth Young Master,

707
00:42:48,165 --> 00:42:49,667
Deliver this letter to Su He.

708
00:42:50,301 --> 00:42:50,568
Yes, sir.

709
00:42:50,801 --> 00:42:51,801
My lord,

710
00:42:59,476 --> 00:43:00,476
Young Master Pei,

711
00:43:00,577 --> 00:43:02,446
We had an agreement back then.

712
00:43:02,646 --> 00:43:04,014
You help my aunt make money,

713
00:43:04,081 --> 00:43:05,281
my aunt helps you raise private troops,

714
00:43:05,282 --> 00:43:06,642
gather information from all over,

715
00:43:06,884 --> 00:43:08,886
and even gives you
a tavern to transmit intelligence.

716
00:43:09,620 --> 00:43:11,255
But you know my aunt.

717
00:43:11,422 --> 00:43:12,732
If she doesn't want to do something,

718
00:43:12,756 --> 00:43:14,316
no amount of money will make her do it.

719
00:43:14,858 --> 00:43:16,160
What does Boss Lin mean by that?

720
00:43:25,769 --> 00:43:26,870
In peaceful times,

721
00:43:27,237 --> 00:43:28,504
you transport goods from Talhan

722
00:43:28,505 --> 00:43:29,673
to sell in our Lin's stores,

723
00:43:29,907 --> 00:43:31,274
I do the work after making money,

724
00:43:31,275 --> 00:43:32,443
and we're both happy.

725
00:43:32,676 --> 00:43:35,012
But if you collude with your uncle,

726
00:43:35,125 --> 00:43:37,103
work together from inside and outside to
disturb the borders of our Daxing,

727
00:43:37,147 --> 00:43:40,217
then wouldn't my aunt be
shooting herself in the foot?

728
00:43:41,085 --> 00:43:42,085
What do you mean?

729
00:43:42,419 --> 00:43:43,419
Don't trust my lord?

730
00:43:45,089 --> 00:43:47,169
I thought the person in
charge of the Jiangnan Lin's

731
00:43:47,458 --> 00:43:48,458
would understand

732
00:43:48,759 --> 00:43:50,270
the principle of trusting those you employ

733
00:43:50,294 --> 00:43:51,662
and not employing those you doubt.

734
00:43:52,296 --> 00:43:53,664
But if Boss Lin

735
00:43:53,964 --> 00:43:55,366
also believes every rumor,

736
00:43:56,807 --> 00:43:58,668
what's the difference between you
and other merchants?

737
00:43:58,669 --> 00:43:59,669
You...

738
00:44:12,125 --> 00:44:15,167
[Letter stating that the emperor is focused on the
border and is sending troops ASAP to defend them.]

739
00:44:17,287 --> 00:44:18,287
Young Master Pei,

740
00:44:18,389 --> 00:44:19,456
You can't blame my aunt.

741
00:44:20,090 --> 00:44:22,426
One must be extra cautious in such matters.

742
00:44:23,761 --> 00:44:25,081
Then I won't disturb you for now.

743
00:44:26,302 --> 00:44:27,302
Oh, by the way,

744
00:44:27,664 --> 00:44:29,365
the girl you brought today,

745
00:44:29,366 --> 00:44:30,366
Don't worry,

746
00:44:30,501 --> 00:44:31,802
she's not as cunning as you.

747
00:44:32,069 --> 00:44:33,103
She's just here for fun,

748
00:44:33,270 --> 00:44:34,390
she won't find out anything.

749
00:44:44,615 --> 00:44:46,050
Not as cunning as me?

750
00:44:46,383 --> 00:44:47,584
Isn't that an indirect insult?

751
00:44:48,652 --> 00:44:49,772
What kind of person is he?

752
00:45:11,975 --> 00:45:12,409
Aunt,

753
00:45:12,543 --> 00:45:13,410
you can rest assured.

754
00:45:13,411 --> 00:45:15,012
I've already warned that person.

755
00:45:18,048 --> 00:45:20,250
He can't be influenced by you.

756
00:45:20,851 --> 00:45:22,352
He just treats you like a child,

757
00:45:22,820 --> 00:45:24,054
humoring you.

758
00:45:36,900 --> 00:45:37,900
I thought.

759
00:45:38,335 --> 00:45:39,670
I'd have a chance

760
00:45:40,104 --> 00:45:41,405
to see her again in this life.

761
00:45:44,808 --> 00:45:45,808
In the end,

762
00:45:47,511 --> 00:45:48,612
I missed it.

763
00:45:51,749 --> 00:45:52,749
Your Highness,

764
00:45:53,584 --> 00:45:56,024
This is a secret letter captured
near the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

765
00:46:03,527 --> 00:46:05,839
The Emperor of Xing attaches
great importance to border affairs.

766
00:46:05,863 --> 00:46:07,965
He will send soldiers
to garrison there soon.

767
00:46:08,699 --> 00:46:10,139
I hope Uncle will restrain yourself.

768
00:46:10,634 --> 00:46:12,354
Don't lose the big picture for small gains.

769
00:46:13,470 --> 00:46:14,910
This is indeed Yanzhi's handwriting.

770
00:46:15,672 --> 00:46:16,440
Your Highness,

771
00:46:16,673 --> 00:46:18,073
This matter is of great importance.

772
00:46:18,208 --> 00:46:21,422
It seems that Young Master Pei has
been sending messages to Su He all along.

773
00:46:22,198 --> 00:46:23,318
Could it be that all of this

774
00:46:23,413 --> 00:46:24,781
didn't happen in the three years

775
00:46:24,782 --> 00:46:25,883
after I left,

776
00:46:26,350 --> 00:46:27,618
but was premeditated long ago?

777
00:46:28,652 --> 00:46:29,253
Let's go.

778
00:46:29,653 --> 00:46:30,693
To the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

779
00:46:30,921 --> 00:46:31,921
Yes, sir.

780
00:46:35,793 --> 00:46:36,793
My lord,

781
00:46:37,161 --> 00:46:38,671
The messenger who
secretly returned to the capital

782
00:46:38,695 --> 00:46:39,429
brought this back for you.

783
00:46:39,496 --> 00:46:40,496
Here you are.

784
00:46:42,566 --> 00:46:44,126
Big brother gave me the military token.

785
00:46:44,968 --> 00:46:45,968
He's afraid

786
00:46:47,371 --> 00:46:49,106
he can't resist Su He's offensive,

787
00:46:50,174 --> 00:46:51,174
and is placing his hopes

788
00:46:51,275 --> 00:46:53,243
on me, who is far away in the capital.

789
00:46:53,911 --> 00:46:55,845
Su He's power is growing stronger now.

790
00:46:55,846 --> 00:46:57,180
Some unscrupulous ministers

791
00:46:57,181 --> 00:46:58,248
are flocking to him.

792
00:46:58,816 --> 00:46:59,216
My lord,

793
00:46:59,626 --> 00:47:00,793
what you're planning now

794
00:47:00,818 --> 00:47:02,486
is all for the future of Talhan.

795
00:47:03,153 --> 00:47:05,473
The Great Khan will definitely
support you wholeheartedly.

796
00:47:10,827 --> 00:47:12,107
Let's go inside and take a look.

797
00:47:15,199 --> 00:47:16,266
Really?

798
00:47:17,801 --> 00:47:18,635
That's not the case at all.

799
00:47:18,635 --> 00:47:19,102
That's not the case.

800
00:47:19,169 --> 00:47:19,770
Come in and sit for a while.

801
00:47:19,803 --> 00:47:22,005
This tavern is definitely
not an ordinary one.

802
00:47:22,973 --> 00:47:24,184
I'll go up and take a look first.

803
00:47:24,208 --> 00:47:25,208
Wait for me here.

804
00:47:25,576 --> 00:47:26,896
If there's a trap in this tavern,

805
00:47:27,044 --> 00:47:27,477
how can I

806
00:47:27,978 --> 00:47:29,246
let you risk your life alone?

807
00:47:29,680 --> 00:47:30,680
Don't worry.

808
00:47:30,781 --> 00:47:32,416
Even if Yanzhi has many secrets,

809
00:47:32,816 --> 00:47:34,017
he won't harm me.

810
00:47:35,185 --> 00:47:35,619
Duan Yong,

811
00:47:35,886 --> 00:47:36,587
Ziming,

812
00:47:36,887 --> 00:47:38,087
you go inside and take a look.

813
00:47:38,155 --> 00:47:39,155
Yes, sir.

814
00:47:48,198 --> 00:47:49,198
Sir,

815
00:47:49,399 --> 00:47:50,677
The private rooms on the second floor

816
00:47:50,701 --> 00:47:53,021
can only be accessed by invitation
from regular customers.

817
00:48:00,077 --> 00:48:00,444
Brother...

818
00:48:00,445 --> 00:48:02,246
Why are you here, brother?

819
00:48:04,848 --> 00:48:05,949
I'll explain to you later.

820
00:48:06,984 --> 00:48:08,024
Help your brother with a favor.

821
00:48:20,864 --> 00:48:23,232
Help! Thief!

822
